/// Test group: input controls
/// Test purpose: sample selection based on an internal random generator
///
/// Test description:
/// Press repeatedly any key. Observe different regions playing in 
/// a random basis (pitch changes on each new note).
///
/// This function allows to arrange several samples for the same note, and 
/// trigger them randomly, for instance, to simulate the small performance
/// variations in each snare hit or violin note.

<group>
sample=..\..\samples\bd.wav 

<region> transpose=0 lorand=0 	 hirand=0.25
<region> transpose=3 lorand=0.25 hirand=0.5
<region> transpose=6 lorand=0.5  hirand=0.75
<region> transpose=8 lorand=0.75 hirand=1
